example.statement:
Write the domain of the following functions, in interval notation.



		f(x) = \dfrac{1}{x}




		g(x) = \dfrac{2x^3 - 1}{x^5 + 1}




		h(x) = \dfrac{6x^4 + x^3 - 7x^2 + 6.5029}{x^2 - 9}

